'''Narmox''' was a small company that specialized in the production of control systems for various models of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], such as the [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing starfighter]] or the [[Z-95 Headhunter/Legends|Z-95 Headhunter]]. The company reached the height of its success during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

